erest declared its opposition to sanctions on russia as of june  arcelormittal accounted for  percent of world steel production after being shut out of the chinese steel industry in  along with other foreign companies in  the company announced it was planning new plants in china in  the company had an annual crude steel production of  million tons  price fixing convictionsedit following an investigation first launched in  in august  the south african competition commission found the company guilty of price fixing arcelormittal was fined us million and as part of the settlement also agreed to invest r billion in capital over five years according to the findings the firm had been part of a  steel member groups nicknamed club zürich that later became known as club europe between january  and september  the companies fixed the market prices and exchanged confidential corporate information according to a european union commission vicepresident it was amazing how the cartel abused nearly the entire european construction market for such a long time and for such a vital product fines were particularly high for the firm owing to two prior convictionscitation needed  recent acquisitionsedit in  the company had a net loss of  billion between february  and february  share value dropped  making the company the worst performer in the ftseurofirst index the ceo said the company had performed poorly in  due to chinese exports depressing prices early in  the company announced it had raised  billion in new investment capital to help reduce debt to  billion of debt in early  the company also announced a program to boost core profit by  billion by  through a mixture of costcutting increased production and a focus on highervalue forms of steel chairman lakshmi mittal announced doubled earnings the following year in may  along with the increase in capital the company also sold its  stake in gestamp automacion for  million with the goal of reducing arcelormittals debt to less than  billio